      "recording_id": "39597e7d-1dab-4711-98bb-1c196332cad8",
      "end_time": 114.42,
      "start_time": 81.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "da6170d1-06f1-4471-a868-4fb3d12f47ae",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "they they're they're stealing information that they should not have a right to get. So the question is are technically they're exempt under the federal law which is in the process of being challenged anyway, we'll probably eventually get to the Spring court. But the question is then if me, as a businessman uses the information that they're selling to me, am I liable to tenants and"
