      "start_time": 114.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "da6170d1-06f1-4471-a868-4fb3d12f47ae",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "the answer to that by my attorney says yes. So I mean are they are they gonna provide more information than what they already have on the map, which is what you can generally get anywhere"
    },
